  a) U.I.A.A. °ê»Úµn¤s»PÃkµnÁp·ù
              Union Internationale des Associations d'Alpinisme
              International Mountaineering and Climbing Federation
              (http://www.mountaineering.org/)

      WHAT IS THE UIAA?
      It is the organisation that represents several million mountaineers and climbers,
      world-wide, on international issues. Formed in 1932 it now has over 80 member
      Associations from some 60 countries, all of national importance. It is recognised
      by the International Olympic Committee IOC as the International Federation
      representing mountaineering and climbing.

