  a). ³Ì¦nªºÃk©¥§Þ¥©¡]§Þ³N»P¾Ô³N¡^½m²ß´N¬O¥hÃk©¥¡C
      The best training for climbing skill (technique and tactics) is climbing.

  b). Ãk©¥§Þ¥©¬O¨Ì¾Ú©¥¥ÛºØÃþ¡A¨¤«×¡A¤Î¼¯À¿¤j¤p¤TÄÝ©Ê¨Ó¬É©w¡C
